# Verification Engine Overhaul — Walkthrough

## Problem
Fake headlines like **"India won World War 4"** and **"PM MODI Died"** were getting incorrectly classified as "Needs Caution" (19%) and "Verified" (49%).

## Root Cause
- Thresholds too low (20% = Verified)
- No absurdity detection
- Keyword overlap inflated by single common words ("Modi" → "Lalit Modi" = 49%)
- Wikipedia/reference matches weighted same as AP/Reuters

## Changes Made

### 1. [verification_engine.dart](file:///c:/Users/devic/AndroidStudioProjects/sachcheck/lib/services/verification_engine.dart) — Complete Rewrite

**6 new scoring layers:**
| Layer | What it does |
|-------|-------------|
| Absurdity detection | Flags death hoaxes, fabricated events (WW4), clickbait patterns |
| Semantic subject matching | "PM Modi Died" vs "Lalit Modi" → subjects don't match → 75% penalty |
| Headline coverage | <40% of headline keywords in article → 50% penalty |
| Source-tier weighting | Wikipedia × 0.55, Established × 1.0, Unknown × 0.5 |
| Weighted keyword overlap | Longer words count more than short ones |
| Consensus scoring | 3+ high-match sources = +5% confidence bonus |

**Raised thresholds:** 55% for Verified (was 20%), 30% for Caution (was 8%)

### 2. [verification_result.dart](file:///c:/Users/devic/AndroidStudioProjects/sachcheck/lib/models/verification_result.dart)
- Added `confidenceLevel` field (`"High"`, `"Medium"`, `"Low"`)
- Added `flags` field (`List<String>`) for absurdity warnings
- Expanded established sources to **40+ outlets** (NDTV, India Today, Zee News, Republic, The Quint, etc.)

### 3. [news_api_service.dart](file:///c:/Users/devic/AndroidStudioProjects/sachcheck/lib/services/news_api_service.dart)
- Added 4 new dedicated Indian source fetchers via Google News RSS site-filter:
  - **NDTV**, **Hindustan Times**, **India Today**, **Times of India**
- Total sources now: **10** (was 6)

### 4. [result_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/devic/AndroidStudioProjects/sachcheck/lib/screens/result/result_screen.dart)
- Warning flags displayed below headline (amber bordered cards)
- Confidence level badge next to match score
- 4 new source pills in "Checked on" row

